mother can
dream about the child with God.

12:36.623 --> 12:39.792 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
What I would like to say, what I
would have
liked to have seen -- and we
talked about

12:39.826 --> 12:44.530 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
structures of sin -- is the
consideration
that perhaps how society is set
up to make

12:44.564 --> 12:50.003 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
the male as the model of
perfection is actually
something that is contrary to us
as women.

12:50.036 --> 12:55.642 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
So, that is why we think that
our fertility
or motherhood is the enemy of
our progress.

12:55.675 --> 12:59.746 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
It's a lot of times because of
how high society
