that awesome
gift that you have.

13:27.607 --> 13:32.879 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
If the human person -- if the
economy exists
to serve the human person, so
much so that

13:32.912 --> 13:36.582 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
the economy exists to serve the
human family,
and we need to make sure women
can participate

13:36.616 --> 13:38.317 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
in that economy.

13:38.351 --> 13:41.821 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
JUDY WOODRUFF: Marianne
Duddy-Burke, what
effect do you think, what
practical effect

13:41.854 --> 13:47.593 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
do you think this is going to
have? He spoke
about the role of individual
priests in interpreting

13:47.627 --> 13:51.297 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
