dogmatic
interaction with people across
the board.

14:13.619 --> 14:18.958 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
I hope that, you know, there's
more of a sense
that the church is first and
foremost here

14:18.991 --> 14:23.730 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
to help care for people and help
us care for
each other, and that that really
needs to

14:23.763 --> 14:25.531 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
be the starting point.

14:25.565 --> 14:30.369 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And I think there is a lot of
that kind of
language there. I think that we
really have

14:30.403 --> 14:34.373 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
to see what the response is
going to be certainly
at the level of the bishops and
cardinals,

14:34.407 --> 14:39.112 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
because that trickles down to
what happens
