another.

14:47.754 --> 14:49.622 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
JUDY WOODRUFF: Right.

14:49.655 --> 14:54.594 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
MARIANNE DUDDY-BURKE: So, that
