16:21.247 --> 16:24.784 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: And, Gloria
Purvis, what do
you see changing as a result of
this?

16:24.817 --> 16:28.521 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
GLORIA PURVIS: Well, I think,
really, it's
a challenge to the priests,
because it is

16:28.554 --> 16:35.261 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
