compassionate to waive the
teaching to make

16:47.340 --> 16:49.208 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
people feel comfortable.

16:49.242 --> 16:52.912 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
I think what the pope is calling
the priests
to do is to walk with each of
the sheep wherever

16:52.945 --> 16:58.317 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
