holiness,
which means properly forming our
conscience

16:58.351 --> 17:02.488 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
and being willing to listen. And
the priest
is going to have to be a bride
of Christ and

17:02.521 --> 17:07.660 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
have the heart of a mother in
dealing with
some very troubled children. So,
that's what

17:07.693 --> 17:09.495 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
I think is going to change.

17:09.528 --> 17:13.466 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: Well, we thank
all three of
you for helping us look through,
think through

17:13.499 --> 17:18.070 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
