approaches to criminal justice.

17:56.142 --> 18:04.050 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JEFFREY BROWN: The William C.
Holman maximum
security prison in Atmore,
Alabama loud, crowded,

18:04.083 --> 18:09.889 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
and, when we visited just weeks
