break it up was stabbed, as was
the warden.

18:23.269 --> 18:29.942 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Video uploaded to Facebook by an
inmate using
a smuggled cell phone captured
some of the

18:29.976 --> 18:31.877 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
mayhem.

18:31.911 --> 18:38.918 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And it took the prison's rapid
response emergency
squads to reestablish order. It
was a shocking

18:38.951 --> 18:43.322 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
that unfolded here at Holman
Correctional
Facility on March 11 were, but
perhaps more

18:43.356 --> 18:47.827 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
shocking is that no one we have
spoken to
is surprised that something like
this could

18:47.860 --> 18:49.695 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
