penal reform
bill passed last year by an
overwhelming majority

19:36.809 --> 19:41.547 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
in the Republican-controlled
legislature,
and signed into law by the
Republican governor.

19:41.580 --> 19:45.484 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
GOV. ROBERT BENTLEY: I know, in
Alabama, just
like in a lot of states, it was
a three strikes

19:45.518 --> 19:51.090 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
