at that. We need to look at a
different approach.

19:56.562 --> 19:59.165 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
And that's what we're doing in
the state with
our prison reform bill.

19:59.198 --> 20:03.135 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JEFFREY BROWN: Republican State
Senator Cam
Ward spearheaded the legislative
effort.

20:03.169 --> 20:05.638 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
CAM WARD (R), Alabama State
Senator: It took
many years to get into this
mess; it's going

20:05.671 --> 20:09.942 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
