violations.

20:56.388 --> 21:01.594 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
For the first time, the new law
uses risk
assessment to focus resources on
those who

21:01.627 --> 21:06.632 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
