treatment and
mental health programs for those
released

21:06.665 --> 21:08.534 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
under correctional supervision.

21:08.567 --> 21:12.438 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
CAM WARD: Ninety-eight percent
of everybody
who's an inmate in a prison
today in the United

21:12.471 --> 21:15.941 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
States eventually gets released.
