had to deal or hear people about
this. And

21:49.542 --> 21:53.078 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
then, finally, I would say,
myself, I look
at it from a legal aspect.
You're going to

21:53.112 --> 21:57.917 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
