Amendment to the Constitution
if you continuing running
facilities and a

21:57.950 --> 21:59.785 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
system like we have been.

21:59.818 --> 22:03.522 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JEFFREY BROWN: The Eighth
Amendment prohibits
punishment considered cruel and
unusual and

22:03.556 --> 22:06.725 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
