motivates
Ward and many others.

22:06.759 --> 22:10.362 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
BRYAN STEVENSON, Founder, Equal
Justice Initiative:
I think it is cruel and I think
it's unusual.

22:10.396 --> 22:12.164 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
I think it violates the Eighth
Amendment.

22:12.198 --> 22:16.569 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JEFFREY BROWN: Bryan Stevenson
is a lawyer
and prison reform activist who
founded the

22:16.602 --> 22:22.441 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Equal Justice Initiative, a
Montgomery-based
nonprofit that represents
prisoners and indigent

22:22.474 --> 22:26.979 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
defendants. He says the state's
reform efforts
