ago in Alabama,
the judge had to impose a
mandatory life without

24:24.663 --> 24:26.432 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
parole sentence on this man.

24:26.465 --> 24:30.102 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
