thousands of people
in jails and prisons who don't
need to there.

24:45.250 --> 24:47.286 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
And we haven't found the courage
yet to get
them out.

24:47.319 --> 24:51.991 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
GOV. ROBERT BENTLEY: We're very
proud of how
we have taken this facility and
done some

24:52.024 --> 24:55.861 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
work in it. It still has
considerable limitations.

24:55.894 --> 25:01.166 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JEFFREY BROWN: Even if the new
reforms do
work, they will only limit the
overcrowding.

