outdated facilities like
Tutwiler.

25:11.477 --> 25:17.082 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
GOV. ROBERT BENTLEY: The
facilities we have
right now with 190 percent
occupancy rate,

25:17.116 --> 25:24.089 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
