the prisoners,

25:24.123 --> 25:29.228 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
to our corrections officers, and
really to
the public, and it's costing us
hundreds of

25:29.261 --> 25:31.029 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
millions of dollars.

25:31.063 --> 25:36.935 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And so we can modernize the
system, and we
can try to correct and help
those who are

25:36.969 --> 25:38.670 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
here, and that's our goal.

25:38.704 --> 25:42.341 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JEFFREY BROWN: But now the
