does that have
any impact, do you think, on
your potential

26:01.960 --> 26:04.229 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
to pass reform, prison reform?

26:04.263 --> 26:08.567 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
GOV. ROBERT BENTLEY: You know, I
