to solve problems, just like I'm
trying to

26:20.946 --> 26:22.047 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
do.

26:22.080 --> 26:23.816 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JEFFREY BROWN: And how big a
priority is this
for you?

26:23.849 --> 26:27.586 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
GOV. ROBERT BENTLEY: This is
very high. This
is -- right now is my highest
priority.

26:27.619 --> 26:29.388 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
JEFFREY BROWN: Highest?

26:29.421 --> 26:32.257 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
GOV. ROBERT BENTLEY: Highest
