the closest right now to solving
this problem

26:32.291 --> 26:37.196 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
that will solve a problem for
the state of
Alabama for the next 30 to 50
years. And that's

26:37.229 --> 26:41.200 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
