28:00.212 --> 28:04.883 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
And a warning: The story
contains images some
viewers may find disturbing.

28:04.917 --> 28:10.022 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
NICK SCHIFRIN: On Kenya's front
line against
Al-Shabaab, police on patrol are
armed like

28:10.055 --> 28:17.429 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
