traditional straw houses,
checking I.D.s at the barrel of
a gun.

28:17.462 --> 28:20.399 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JULIUS KIRAGU, Kenyan Army
(through translator):
The main threat here is the
Al-Shabaab. That

28:20.432 --> 28:24.903 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
