31:07.232 --> 31:11.470 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
NICK SCHIFRIN: What is the main
goal for you
and your men in al-Shabaab?

31:11.503 --> 31:15.407 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
MAN (through translator): We
want to have
an Islamic State in Somalia,
where Sharia

31:15.440 --> 31:16.675 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
law is practiced.

31:16.708 --> 31:19.344 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
NICK SCHIFRIN: Why you have
launched attacks
inside Kenya?

31:19.377 --> 31:23.014 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
MAN (through translator): Kenya
has invaded
our land.

31:23.048 --> 31:27.853 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
NICK SCHIFRIN: Shabaab claims to
be fighting
for Kenyan Muslims. It recruits
Kenyans to

31:27.886 --> 31:33.859 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
carry out attacks in Kenya. The
worst in 20
years was on Garissa University.

31:33.892 --> 31:36.795 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
How bad was the scene here when
you arrived?

31:36.828 --> 31:38.663 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
HAMO MOHAMED, Garissa
University: It was terrible.

31:38.697 --> 31:43.135 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
NICK SCHIFRIN: Hamo Mohamed is
Garissa's dean
of students. This classroom is
still scarred

31:43.168 --> 31:48.607 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
