murdered
19 students in this room for
singing Christian

31:48.640 --> 31:50.408 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
prayers.

31:50.442 --> 31:55.781 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
HAMO MOHAMED: Bodies of the
students that
you know them by names, the
young, aspiring,

31:55.814 --> 31:59.351 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
and you're seeing their body
lying down, you
know, their blood all over.

31:59.384 --> 32:05.056 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
SOFIE GATRIWIRI, Student: They
came when I
was here, and then I would be no
more too.

32:05.090 --> 32:07.092 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
So I'm just lucky.

32:07.125 --> 32:09.161 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
NICK SCHIFRIN: Sofie Gatriwiri
is a junior.

32:09.194 --> 32:12.764 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
SOFIE GATRIWIRI: I'm going to
finish my education
and get a better job.

32:12.798 --> 32:16.201 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
NICK SCHIFRIN: She was a member
of the Christian
prayer group that was attacked.

32:16.234 --> 32:18.236 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
How many friends did you lose?

32:18.270 --> 32:23.575 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
SOFIE GATRIWIRI: I lost like 15.
I don't like
this discussing that story about
those people,

32:23.608 --> 32:27.112 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
those students who passed. I
don't like at
all.

32:27.145 --> 32:32.317 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
NICK SCHIFRIN: The gunmen lured
the students
down into this courtyard, right?

32:32.350 --> 32:37.189 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
